refentry.refsect1:
   Description

     mixedcom_get
     resourcecom_object
     stringproperty



    Returns the value of the property of the
    COM component referenced by com_object.
    Returns &false; on error.




     Don't use com_get(), use OO syntax instead


<?php 
// do this
$var = $obj->property;
// instead of this:
$var = com_get($obj, 'property');
?>





  &reference.com.use-oo-instead;
